Job.create!([
  {title: "Front End Web designer", description: "<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">We are looking to showcase our technology on our website, bringing the power of speech recognition to users through the browser.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">A large part of the work will be in designing and developing new ways to use speech recognition in the browser, with emphasis on creating a clean, responsive and intuitive user experience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">The focus of this role will be on the front end, but you will be involved in all layers of the stack.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">We are looking for engineers with at least 2-3 years of experience in designing and building front end web applications.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">An ideal candidate would possess the following:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Full stack web development experience</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Proven portfolio of successful UI/UX projects</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Extensive HTML/CSS/AJAX/Javascript (jQuery, Angular, require/browserify, meteor) coding experience</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">CSS compiler knowledge (E.g., Sass, LESS)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Experience debugging front-ends</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">A strong, traditional belief in clean and beautiful code. No exceptions.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Strict discipline in following existing formatting standards</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Comfortable working on tight deadlines and in a team environment</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Comfortable with version control</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Comfortable using modern technologies and interfacing with existing libraries</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">No prior speech recognition experience is expected &ndash; we have a team of developers who build and maintain the speech recognition back end.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", company: "Speechmatics", salary: 35000, url: "#"},
  {title: "Web Developer - LAMP - Front-end Focus", description: "<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">Due Diligence Checking Ltd. are looking for a talented web developer who is ready to make a big contribution to a rapidly growing company. We want you to be innovative, open to fresh ideas and ambitious. You will have access to the full range of technologies we employ, and you will get the opportunity to shape future developments.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">We are looking to recruit a front-end focussed web developer to join our in-house web development team. Your primary responsibility will be for designing and shaping our user interface and refining our front-end code workflow. We use modern tools, such as Foundation, Vagrant and SCSS, and we are looking for someone who can create perfectly-formed layouts, with efficiency and consistency. As well as working with the front-end, there will be ample opportunity to gain experience with the full application stack, and learn how to solve view layer problems within an MVC application.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">We are a small team, but we work hard and we work together. We use slack, Gtalk, and an internal ticketing system to keep things running smoothly. We adopt new technologies when they are useful, and we have recently moved to Mercurial/RhodeCode and deployed TeamCity to run our builds for us. We also get together once a month in East London, to talk tech, eat some good food and to plan how to improve our architecture.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Job Details:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Permanent role, with 6-month probationary period</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">&pound;23-26,000 pa, (plus project-based bonuses after the 1st year)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">40 hours per week</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Office-based in Syston (North Leicestershire)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Start date &ndash; ASAP</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Job Advertisement: 20th Feb. 2016</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">1-3 years&rsquo; relevant experience, or a computer science degree</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Must have right to work in UK</li>\r\n</ul>", company: "Due Diligence Checking Ltd", salary: 28000, url: "#"},
  {title: "Python Full Stack Developer ", description: "<div class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">We&rsquo;re looking for an experienced full stack developer who&rsquo;d like the chance to convert their existing skills to Ruby.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">We might just be Oxfordshire&rsquo;s best-kept secret, in a beautiful location with a wide range of innovative and challenging projects for some brilliant clients (e.g. BMW, Barclays, Rolls-Royce and InterContinental Hotels). We work on rich, interactive, single-page web apps, in a forward-thinking Agile development environment with the latest technologies and processes (making sure we use the right tool for the job), and we&rsquo;re looking for a talented full stack developer to join us.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">We work in a Ruby environment, so we&rsquo;re looking for someone who&rsquo;s interested in transferring their Python (or similar) skills to Ruby. We will give you a dedicated training budget, time to get to grips with Ruby, and plenty of time pair programming in a team of highly experienced Ruby devs. In return, you&rsquo;ll have 4+ years of commercial experience, working in projects on both front end (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery) and back end (Python, Linux, Heroku, PostgreSQL) and though you may have a natural leaning towards one or the other, you&rsquo;ll be passionate about using and extending your skills across the whole development platform.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">Your personality is important to us too. You&rsquo;ll be well-organised with the ability to&nbsp;prioritise and multi-task day-to-day. A sense of humour and a sense of perspective would be hugely beneficial too. As would a love of cake.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">We are relatively small company (20 Juicers) and all parts of the business work closely&nbsp;together,&nbsp;so experience of working within a similar production/agency background would be very beneficial.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class=\"detail-sectionTitle\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 30px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.15385; font-weight: 400; color: #606d76; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">Skills &amp; Requirements</h2>\r\n<div class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">An excellent understanding of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery and associated front-end technologies and tools, including experience with AngularJS, React, ES6 or similar</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">An excellent understanding of Python, Django, Linux, Heroku, AWS and associated back end tools and technologies</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">A solid understanding of networking tools and technologies such as SSH and VPN</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Proven experience of testing approaches such as TDD and BDD</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">A strong understanding of mobile web development, debugging and optimisation (Native app development an advantage)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Solid experience of Git for version control</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">An excellent understanding of database technologies, object-orientated programming and design patterns (PostgreSQL a distinct advantage)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Conscientious and team focused, happy with peer review and pair programming.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>", company: "Juice Moving Images Ltd", salary: 32000, url: "#"},
  {title: "Creative full stack developer", description: "<div class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">We are building interesting things using ReactJS and ASP.net MVC 5 and would like you on our team!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">This is an exciting opportunity for a junior to mid-level, full stack developer with a passion for the front-end and making things work on mobile. Working in a skilled, close-knit agile team, you will play an important role in creating a mixture of new projects and delivering new features to current ones, in line with our design guidelines and architecture principles.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">We would also like you to develop your skills to by pairing with others and to ensure best practice is being followed within the agile&nbsp;team. Our version of agile involves standups, retrospectives, poker, hack days and show and tells.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />You&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">MUST</span>&nbsp;be currently&nbsp;based&nbsp;in the UK to apply for this position. Within the UK, we are flexible on remote working.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class=\"detail-sectionTitle\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 30px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.15385; font-weight: 400; color: #606d76; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">Skills &amp; Requirements</h2>\r\n<div class=\"description\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; clear: both;\">&bull; People who are confident and at a proficient level of C# and JavaScript (Ideally people with at least 3 years&rsquo; experience). We would expect people to be able to demonstrate their ability during the interview process.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Experience of building Rest-like API&rsquo;s using technologies such as ASP.NET Web API 2 or Node JS.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Building front-end JavaScript applications ideally using React/Redux, also experience of front-end build processes.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Effective knowledge of clean code, understanding of SOLID principles, can demonstrate software design patterns in multiple languages.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Experience of test-driven methodologies.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Have experience working in an agile environment.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Is effective at managing own time and learning.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Happy in a variety of IDEs such as Visual Studio 2015, WebStorm, Brackets or Code.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Has experience of relational databases including SQL Server 2014+.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\" />&bull; Experience of GIT version control</p>\r\n</div>", company: "Contact Group", salary: 40000, url: "#"},
  {title: "Badly Dressed Junior PHP Developer", description: "<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Role Responsibility</span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">You will be responsible for maintaining and improving our data processing platform (Millions Docs processed every day)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">You will help maintain very heavy traffic Web Services (thousand requests per second)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\">Building the next generation data processing platform and web services.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">The Ideal Candidate</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Essential:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Basic experience of PHP 5&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Solid basis of Object Orientated Programming&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Good understanding of Linux environments: Bash programming, daemons etc.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Basic understanding of Regular Expressions&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Git /SVN experience&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Ability to work independently and in a team&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 13px 26px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; border: 0px; line-height: 1.46154;\">Have a keen eye for details and work to a high standard&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 13px; clear: both; color: #40484f; font-family: Arial, HelveticaNeue-Regular, 'Helvetica Neue Regular', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; line-height: 19px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Desirable:</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul s